                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Order Placed!</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Thank you for choosing Shudhh Sattu. Your order ID is <span class="font-mono font-bold text-brand">#SS9821</span></p>
